{
  "texts": [
    "Third, many computation resources are needed for deep CNN training, which often necessitates a lot of specialists' prolonged devotion 18.",
    "The pathologist's manual brain cancer diagnosis is time-consuming, exhausting, and burdensome.",
    "Few studies have been conducted to determine the grade of a brain tumor 19.",
    "On the other hand, established automated systems that aid pathologists in cancer grade categorization depend on human-crafted feature tools that burden developers 20.",
    "In addition to the richness and complexity of the retrieved features, these methods are sensitive to noise, contrast, and staining in digital histology images."
  ]
}